---
title: One-pot Curried Chicken Rice				 with broccoli and mint raita
description: One-pot dishes are great for a myriad of reasons. They're simple to prepare, they lock in lots of flavour, and there's less washing up to do at the end of it all. Sounds like an all-round winning dinner!
